; Test auto xact cost derivation with ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT and negative sign
; Exercises lines 1125-1127 of xact.cc

= Expenses:Energy
    (Budget:Energy)    1

2024/01/01 Sell energy
    Expenses:Energy    -100 kWh {{72 EUR}} @@ 72 EUR
    Assets:Cash        72 EUR

test reg Budget:Energy
24-Jan-01 Sell energy           (Budget:Energy)            -100 kWh     -100 kWh
end test
